_sText:
This is my first map other than the "simple-room-map" I started with to learn Hammer Editor. :-P

This is a short beginner map with a few things to discover. If you know how to make secret doors (looks like wall, but can go through it), please PM me. :-D

Please write constructive critism, as I'm still in the newbie stage of map making. I may soon start working on a surf map.

You can do whatever you want with this map, just give me credits.

##############INSTALLATION##################

Copy the BSP file called "fy_chralle" to:
C:/Programs/Steam/SteamApps/your_name/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps

############################################

If you have any problems, let me know.
